=============================================
README for the IBM_DB2 and PDO_IBM Extensions
=============================================
The IBM_DB2 and PDO_IBM are the PHP extensions for IBM DataServers. Installing the IBM_DB2 or PDO_IBM extensions enables any application in the PHP environment to interact with IBM data servers.

The extensions available with this DB2 package might be of a lower version as compared to the one available on the community. It is recommended that you download the latest extension available on the PECL page of IBM_DB2 (http://pecl.php.net/package/ibm_db2) and PDO_IBM (http://pecl.php.net/package/pdo_ibm), as it might contain important fixes and new features.

Installing the IBM_DB2 and PDO_IBM extensions
=============================================

On Linux, UNIX, and Mac OS X
----------------------------
Following links explain how to install PECL extensions

Through source code       :     http://www.php.net/manual/en/install.pecl.phpize.php
Through PECL command      :     http://www.php.net/manual/en/install.pecl.pear.php

Installing IBM_DB2 extension
----------------------------
http://www.php.net/manual/en/ibm-db2.installation.php

Installing PDO_IBM extension
----------------------------
http://www.php.net/pdo_ibm

Windows
-------
Download latest binaries  :     http://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=211760&package_id=327473

